      • putTemplate

        public void putTemplate(String name,
               String locale,
               String templateSource)
        Puts a template into the loader. A call to this method is identical to the call to the putTemplate(String, String, String, long) passing System.currentTimeMillis() as the fourth argument.
        Parameters:
        name - the name of the template.
        locale - locale
        templateSource - the source code of the template.

      • putTemplate

        public void putTemplate(String name,
               String locale,
               String templateSource,
               long lastModified)
        Puts a template into the loader. A call to this method is identical to the call to the StringTemplateLoader.putTemplate(String, String, long) passing System.currentTimeMillis() as the third argument.
        Parameters:
        name - the name of the template.
        locale - locale
        templateSource - the source code of the template.
        lastModified - the time of last modification of the template in terms of System.currentTimeMillis()
